videos.headline: Phil Booth made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by Jalen Brunson.

videos.description: Eric Paschall gets out in transition and rises up to slam it home for Villanova.
videos.headline: Paschall throws down an emphatic alley-oop slam

videos.description: Donte DiVincenzo puts on a move and gets the bucket for the Wildcats.
videos.headline: DiVincenzo makes tough layup in the lane

videos.description: Jalen Brunson gets left open in transition and makes Xavier pay with a 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Brunson drains transition three

videos.description: Jalen Brunson gets up for the transition slam after picking up the steal for Villanova.
videos.headline: Brunson brings the hammer after a steal

videos.description: Naji Marshall rises up and throws it down with one hand to put a Villanova defender on a poster.
videos.headline: Marshall puts defender on a poster

videos.description: Phil Booth reads the defense, picks off the pass and takes it the other way for the easy dunk.
videos.headline: Booth picks up a steal plus the slam
